{"meta":{"title":"Nodejs Basics","description":"Installing NodeJS & NPM packages","tags":"zyrouge, nodejs, npm","image":"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/9c24355bb3afbff914503b663ade7beb341079fa/68747470733a2f2f6e6f64656a732e6f72672f7374617469632f696d616765732f6c6f676f2d6c696768742e737667","writtenAt":"18 Jun 2020 14:28"},"body":"<h2>Installing NodeJS</h2>\n<p>Download and install from <a href=\"https://nodejs.org\">NodeJS Website</a></p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Creating a Project</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-text\">$ npm init\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2>Installing Modules</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-text\">$ npm install module-name\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2>Installing Globally</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-text\">$ npm install -g module-name\n</code></pre>\n","env":null}